description: Try our easy to follow Spaghetti Marinara recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Marinara,Pescatarian,Quick & easy dinner,Low saturated fat,High protein,Tree nut free,Seafood,Low sugar,Low fat,Peanut free
name: Spaghetti Marinara Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 600g Bag’N’Bake marinara seafood mix with tomato & basil sauce (available from the seafood counter)

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200°C. Cook seafood mix following packet directions.
Meanwhile, cook pasta following packet directions. Drain well and return to saucepan.
Transfer seafood to pan and toss to combine. Garnish with parsley.
